## Slash Commands

For explicit command access, use slash commands:

**Content creation:**
- `/write-blog` - Create a blog article
- `/write-linkedin` - Create a LinkedIn post
- `/write-facebook` - Create a Facebook post
- `/write-instagram` - Create an Instagram caption
- `/write-tweet` - Create a single tweet
- `/write-thread` - Create a Twitter thread
- `/write-seo-meta` - Create SEO and social metadata
- `/write-package` - Create a complete content package
- `/research-content` - Research a topic before writing

**Profile management:**
- `/profile-create` - Create a new writer profile
- `/profile-view` - View current profile
- `/profile-edit` - Edit profile
- `/profile-delete` - Delete profile

**Asset management:**
- `/products-add`, `/products-view`, `/products-edit`, `/products-delete`
- `/ctas-add`, `/ctas-view`, `/ctas-edit`, `/ctas-delete`
- `/cases-add`, `/cases-view`, `/cases-edit`, `/cases-delete`

